# Video Playback Test Coverage Enhancement
Comprehensive test coverage for in-browser video demuxing, decoding, and playback to discover edge cases and prepare for future refactoring. **No implementation changes during this phase.**

## Test plan / verification steps
```bash
# Run existing browser tests (from lib/packages directory)
cd lib/packages
npm run browsertest

# Run existing Node.js tests
npm test -- lib/packages/packages/assets/src/MP4File.test.ts

# Run new browser test suites as they're added
cd lib/packages
npm run browsertest -- --grep "Error scenarios"
npm run browsertest -- --grep "Performance"
npm run browsertest -- --grep "Audio processing"
npm run browsertest -- --grep "Integration"

# Watch mode for development
cd lib/packages
npm run browsertest:watch

# Check test coverage (if available)
npm run test:coverage -- lib/packages/packages/assets/src/
npm run test:coverage -- lib/packages/packages/elements/src/elements/
```

